NARRATIVE:

    On 10/27/2023 at approximately 1049 hours, I was advised by the victim, Lauren Michelle Healy (W/F 06/07/1983), that her Facebook Account: https://www.facebook.com/lnhealy had been contacted by the suspect Facebook Account: "Lauren Harsch" -  https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61552719785801&comment_id=Y29tbWVudDoxMDE2MTM1MTMwNTgxMTk2M182NTU5NDE5MjMzNjEwOTY%3D. Healy suspected the account was being owned/operated by Brian Kelly Motz (W/M 01/28/1980). Healy advised she has previously filed a Protection Order against Motz, however it did not go through given a lack of evidence that she should be "fearful". Healy did provide that "it is on transcript that he was not to contact me". Healy also added that "The judge just made him verbally agree to that in the end". I confirmed with Healy that she has advised Motz not to contact her and she advised "Yes... Numerous times", adding that she has even texted Motz' attorney as well to have Motz not contact and "leave me(her) alone". I reviewed the post Healy was reporting and observe the information listed below:

    Healy posted "Thank you to everyone that has reached out to me. I appreciate your loyalty and friendship. I’m good…just wish that the harassment would stop! I truly believe that people make their own bed and the entire truth will come out in the end. God always prevails!" Shortly after the post, Kara Crum Baker - (Facebook Account: https://www.facebook.com/rob.n.kara?comment_id=Y29tbWVudDoxMDE2MTM1MTMwNTgxMTk2M18yMDIzMDU3ODk0ODcyMjM%3D) replied "STILL with the harassment? How has “this person” not been arrested yet?!‍" and a conversation began between the two and the suspect account, Lauren Harsch - (Facebook Account: https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61552719785801&comment_id=Y29tbWVudDoxMDE2MTM1MTMwNTgxMTk2M182NTU5NDE5MjMzNjEwOTY%3D) posted "Lauren Healy Lies lies". Lauren Healy responded by stating "Lauren Harsch interesting choice for a name since an exes last name is Harscher. Grow up! Move on! You make yourself look stupid and everyone sees it!" A separate conversation between Healy and the suspect account also began after the suspect account replied to the post stating "Maybe you should tell everyone the truth. You continue to tell lies, spread gossip, after you were told by a judge not to! You just cannot stop. Why? Because you got caught? You once posted “justice will be served,” you are so right…the investigation you are a part of is complete. Your claims of harassment are completely baseless as you are the one that is harassing people. And yes, the truth is about to come out. God is good and he knows the plans that he has for all of us!" Healy responded by stating "Lauren Harsch I believe I was the one to take you to court for a peace order. I’m not the one being investigated. Everything you claim I did was completely unfounded. But not yours If you didn’t stalk me, have your mother call and harrass me (which I can happily add the voicemail to this thread) try to hire someone to “take me out” all because I called out your drug use. I know what I know. You definitely know too. This is my Facebook that you have to go on and stalk me. God will get you the help you need." and also added "I have a laundry list of proof so save yourself the embarrassment". The suspect account then responded by stating "Lauren Healy Lol…I’m not sure who you think you are talking to but it seems like you have nothing better to do with your life than post on FB about how pathetic you are". Healy then responded by stating "Lauren Harsch I know who I’m talking to. You jumped on my Facebook not the other way around. I have a right to respond to your ridiculous comments since it’s my Facebook. You’re just mad because I knew your entire life and wouldn’t be one of your pawns that would do things illegally to cover up for you. My rapport is good. Can’t say that about you."
